## Remarks
 <span data-ttu-id="4940f-187">处理 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> 事件以提供您自己 <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> 的，而不是创建新的 <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4940f-187">Handle the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> event to supply your own <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> instead of having a new <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4940f-188">如果 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> 未处理事件或处理程序未提供 <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> ，则将 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource> 根据其配置创建一个。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4940f-188">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> event is not handled or the handler does not provide an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource> creates one according to its configuration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4940f-189"><xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>向事件提供时 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> ，会将相同的实例分配给 `Context` 连续事件的事件对象的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4940f-189">When an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> is provided to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> event, the same instance is assigned to the `Context` property of the event object of successive events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4940f-190">有关详细信息，请参阅 [对象上下文生命周期管理 (EntityDataSource) ](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/aspnet/cc668193(v=vs.100))。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4940f-190">For more information, see [Object Context Life-Cycle Management (EntityDataSource)](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/aspnet/cc668193(v=vs.100)).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4940f-191">有关对象上下文的详细信息，请参阅 [标识解析、状态管理和更改跟踪](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/dotnet/netframework-4.0/bb896269(v=vs.100))。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4940f-191">For more information about the object context, see [Identity Resolution, State Management, and Change Tracking](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/dotnet/netframework-4.0/bb896269(v=vs.100)).</span></span>



## Examples
 <span data-ttu-id="4940f-192">下面的示例演示如何创建对象的 <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> 变量 <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> 并将其分配给 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> 对象的属性 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4940f-192">The following example shows how to create an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> variable of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object and assign it to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object.</span></span>

```csharp
public partial class _Default : System.Web.UI.Page
    {
        AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities objCtx =
            new AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities();

        protected void EntityDataSource2_ContextCreating(object sender,
            EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs e)
        {
            e.Context = objCtx;
        }
    }
```
